c09450c0d20fc1f4978c970e6866279eae7","tid":154620,"uid":16414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T13:28:46.000Z","msg":"政府決定重建觀塘就知個頭啲樓時日無多"},{"pid":"3dc728abb4540964a7df208a7cd4fbc4e7fc62d5","tid":154620,"uid":56561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T13:29:27.000Z","msg":"一個二個話自己幾多年冇食M記<br />\n<br />\n到M記染紅&amp;摺分店，就忽然咁撚有感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c5d6477af9d57828c1c19cb6e6942e221fe6651","tid":154620,"uid":16414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T13:31:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一個二個話自己幾多年冇食M記<br />\n<br />\n到M記染紅&amp;摺分店，就忽然咁撚有感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港邊次唔係咁"},{"pid":"9f275388cb465382ac0d895262baf272a5b5c0aa","tid":154620,"uid":41507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T13:32:40.000Z","msg":"依間可以當選全港最難食m記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"611f7c65a5fd59d7aef2728ca8d0d4e214aaaf61","tid":154620,"uid":32686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T13:34:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有幾唔捨得<br />\n呢間麥當勞臭嘅</blockquote><br />\n真係好撚污糟</blockquote><br />\n早就應該執。 間野臭既！ 我屋企個廁所仲乾淨過佢。<br />\n又臭，地方又污糟。  條樓梯都係尿味。"},{"pid":"e9d9745492449ef1ce3a40cce459b9f130a4f401","tid":154620,"uid":7119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T13:35:29.000Z","msg":"呢間係污糟正賴屎"},{"pid":"04453baad5b773401d63572e99310f4fdc81bfc9","tid":154620,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T13:36:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2fd053a8ce3c92b81551732776082e44e14a926f","tid":154620,"uid":25496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T13:41:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>觀塘另一間老麥摺左之後就一直係個度食 細個會成家咁去食開心樂園餐<br />\nDse雞個時自修室無位就去個度摺 一次過解決一日三餐 同中同由朝坐到黑 私補溫書咩都齊 奮鬥的記憶<br />\n到大少少拍拖無錢又係係個度打躉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係你呢啲仆街食少少嘢霸撚住一日</blockquote><br />\n窮學生邊有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25e11c393852ac1b86955bf3838c03d222bb4388","tid":154620,"uid":329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T13:41:19.000Z","msg":"觀塘凈返翠屏 地牢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63056fbe996876b92dda4c722f14bda56bbde5b9","tid":154620,"uid":15703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T13:43:08.000Z","msg":"觀塘果間臭過公廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n夜晚成堆難民痴線佬"},{"pid":"64bb4f7d180245e7b78e7cd1d7971239e6238048","tid":154620,"uid":22218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T13:43:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一個二個話自己幾多年冇食M記<br />\n<br />\n到M記染紅&amp;摺分店，就忽然咁撚有感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢間唔同<br />\n呢間舊麥記重長命過康寧道果間新麥記<br />\n不過係觀塘撚先會明"},{"pid":"abfb5eaf7bc81817c868fafd32ba39d8d19bf685","tid":154620,"uid":78522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T14:04:19.000Z","msg":"之前山林道執完咪又開返"}]}